se chicken skewers will surprise you. The warm vegetable salad and the carrot and cumin rice transform familiar ingredients into a special meal.<\/i>","For a vegetarian version of this dish, replace chicken with halloumi cheese, cut in cubes (2 cm). Follow the recipe excluding the extra cooking time in <nobr>step 7.<\/nobr><br>- For a spicier dish add <nobr>½-1 tsp<\/nobr> chilli sauce to the marinade ingredients."],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","2h","4 portions"]}